{%- comment -%}
  MY.LAB header block — logo centré + numéro de commande centré en dessous.

  Remplace le fichier order-confirmation-mylab-logo-block.liquid pour ceux
  qui veulent le logo centré.

  HOW TO APPLY:
  1. Dans le template "Confirmation de commande", localiser le bloc :
       <table class="row">
         <tr>
           <td class="shop-name__cell">
             {%- if shop.email_logo_url %}
               <img src="{{shop.email_logo_url}}" alt="{{ shop.name }}" width="{{ shop.email_logo_width }}">
             {%- else %}
               <h1 class="shop-name__text">
                 <a href="{{shop.url}}">{{ shop.name }}</a>
               </h1>
             {%- endif %}
           </td>
             <td>
               <table class="order-po-number__container">
                 <tr>
                   <td class="order-number__cell">
                     <span class="order-number__text">
                       Commande {{ order_name }}
                     </span>
                   </td>
                 </tr>
                 {%- if po_number %}
                     <tr>
                       <td class="po-number__cell">
                         <span class="po-number__text">
                           Bon de commande nº {{ po_number }}
                         </span>
                       </td>
                     </tr>
                 {%- endif %}
               </table>
             </td>
         </tr>
       </table>
  2. Remplacer intégralement par le bloc ci-dessous.
{%- endcomment -%}

<table class="row" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td align="center" style="text-align: center; padding: 8px 0 16px;">
      {%- if shop.email_logo_url %}
        <a href="{{ shop.url }}" style="text-decoration: none;">
          <img src="{{ shop.email_logo_url }}" alt="{{ shop.name }}" width="{{ shop.email_logo_width | default: 160 }}" style="max-width: 180px; height: auto; display: inline-block;">
        </a>
      {%- elsif shop.brand.logo %}
        <a href="{{ shop.url }}" style="text-decoration: none;">
          <img src="{{ shop.brand.logo | image_url: width: 360 }}" alt="{{ shop.name }}" width="140" style="max-width: 140px; height: auto; display: inline-block;">
        </a>
      {%- else %}
        <h1 style="font-family: 'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin: 0;">
          <a href="{{ shop.url }}" style="color: #111111; text-decoration: none;">MY.LAB</a>
        </h1>
      {%- endif %}
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="center" style="text-align: center; padding: 0 0 8px;">
      <span class="order-number__text" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #555555; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase;">
        Commande {{ order_name }}
      </span>
      {%- if po_number %}
        <br>
        <span class="po-number__text" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #888888; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.3px;">
          Bon de commande nº {{ po_number }}
        </span>
      {%- endif %}
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
